data.description: Great Arlington neighborhood home in Indian Land. Open spaces, granite kitchen countertops, stainless steel appliances. Wood floor on the main. Easy outside maintenance, has a fenced back yard, patio and a covered rocking chair front porch. Spacious great room. All bedrooms upstairs along with the laundry room. Garage was converted into Bonus Room downstairs which provides another sitting area, entertainment, or office space. Neighborhood amenities include a clubhouse, pool, fitness center and dog parks. Conveniently located close to shops and restaurants.
